### 5. **Homework Submission & Status Tracking**

**File:** `/Users/guitar/Desktop/website-1-wun-production/src/app/api/homework/route.ts` (POST endpoint)

**How homework is submitted:**

```typescript
export async function POST(request: NextRequest) {
  // ... validation ...

  // Get or create lesson ID for module
  const { data: lesson } = await supabase
    .from('lessons')
    .select('id')
    .eq('module_id', moduleId)
    .order('order', { ascending: true })
    .limit(1)
    .single();

  // Check for existing submission
  const { data: existingSubmissions } = await supabase
    .from('homework_submissions')
    .select('id')
    .eq('user_id', user.id)
    .in('lesson_id', allLessonIds)
    .limit(1);

  // Update or Insert
  if (existingSubmissionId) {
    // Update existing
    await supabase
      .from('homework_submissions')
      .update({
        submission_text: content.trim(),
        submitted_at: new Date().toISOString(),
      })
      .eq('id', existingSubmissionId);
  } else {
    // Create new
    await supabase
      .from('homework_submissions')
      .insert({
        user_id: user.id,
        lesson_id: lesson.id,
        submission_text: content.trim(),
        submitted_at: new Date().toISOString(),
      });
  }
}
```

**Database Table:** `homework_submissions`
- Fields: id, user_id, lesson_id, submission_text, submitted_at, grade, feedback, graded_at, status
- Status values: `'SUBMITTED' | 'REVIEWED' | 'APPROVED'`

